Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.62,0:00:05.13,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From a different point of view, even an imposing\Nwall blocking your path is just a large door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:08.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A baseball came flying in, and a house\Nbecomes a case flipped on its head!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something's not right about this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:11.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:12.80,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:14.68,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:01:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't the editor, Shimaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, don't Well, if it isn't Shimaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what are you here about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you saying, {\i1}Sensei{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:18.48,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Toshihisa Manda (53)\NNovelist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just joking, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about the manuscript, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right, Manda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, don't play jokes on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a real problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The printers can only wait two more hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two hours will be more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I've already finished the climax...}I just have one hurdle left to jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and after that, it just leaves the epilogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please trust me. We've known each other so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Novel{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:03:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to keep an eye on {\i1}Sensei{\i0}!{extended?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let him make a run for it!\NIf he tries to get away, bite him!{possibly, bite him if he tries to get away?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting in the lobby by the lifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please call me when you're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... Two more hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like he can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what he said.\NIt'll probably be all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's what he wrote...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Ace of Teitan Primary School's Class 1-B,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the prince of pitchers{not sure about this word}, Genta Kojima,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:10.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}aims to remain undefeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:14.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Two outs, bases loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:17.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mitsuhiko Tsubaraya's in full form!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:19.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And here's the first pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:22.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Counting... for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ball, the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was awesome, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... {\i1}if{\i0} we were playing football.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to catch the ball in your glove!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't football!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got something against baseball, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!\NTake this seriously, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My bad, my bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:22.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After years of playing football, I'm used to doing everything with my legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They got my neck on the line now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:53.24,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kohei Haramoto (28)\NManda's proteg√©
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you sneak out of a hotel again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...disguised as a valet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really like doing that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they tried to lock me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was the quickest way to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, nobody noticed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you brought Novel{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Novel, Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a kitty... It's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't leave him. Novel\Npanics if one of us isn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...have you finished the manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I polished it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...six hours ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six hours ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I called you from the hotel, you said you just needed a bit more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just messing with you. {You wouldn't stop riding me...}Your voice sounds hilarious when you're desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Haramoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't I at least have a little fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being your ghostwriter can get stressful, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as long as you pay me the big bucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got no complaints!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your latest novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a happy ending, just as you requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, er... Did you talk to your editor about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once I hand this off to him, we're going to have a meeting at my place to discuss the next piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bring him across the street to meet you after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you so much! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But if you get published under your own name, you'll want to quit this gig...}But once you've had your d√©but,\NI'll probably have to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I can keep ghosting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be writing detective novels, which is nothing like what you write!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll even use a different writing style.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A different...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm almost done...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with my d√©but novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to give it a lookover? You'll see, it really feels like it was written by somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soon I'll be a real novelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if my work sells, I'll have more\Nmoney for my collections...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:26.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. You {\i1}are{\i0} quite the collector, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've loved collecting stuff since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the item I want now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is the Akutayama Award for New Writers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're one of the judges, so I'm a shoo-in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I win that one, collecting other\Nawards will be a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of collections, I finally got something else I've been missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It feels so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...to complete the set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nice to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Working ‚Äî\hDo Not Enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Novel! Time to head back to the hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Novel? Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Novel? Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Novel? Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Novel! Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Novel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got to hurry... To hurry back to the hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}? Manda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
