Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! {\i1}Sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:17.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}my alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! Manda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! It's been two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:28.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! Manda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! Manda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just going over my last revision!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... I see! Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Frankly, I've impressed even myself this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thanks for the hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, is Novel{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always comes out to greet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:19.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's awfully quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's sleeping in his carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In his carrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd better get back to the office to look this over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you read it in my room and e-mail it to the printer from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'll save you some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, we can go to my place\Nand talk about my next novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you had anything planned after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:13:02.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an entirely new genre for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you specialize in period fiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not pulling my leg, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I've always wanted to challenge\Nmyself with a mystery novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.\NI can't wait to read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}, please, tell me more about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already thought up a detective character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you all about it at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:44.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, tell me! Don't leave me hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Novel{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is awfully quiet today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was running around all day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:13:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...so he must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to tidy up a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure. I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Novel! Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:37.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Novel, you're back! Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it's all in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've completed the perfect crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:15:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think a window broke in the house across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like some kids were playing baseball and hit a ball into a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:26.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You swing too hard, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it on purpose! It bounced away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't tell the ball where it can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody's answering the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like somebody's at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the ball hit the person inside the house and knocked them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:54.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way to know without going inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling it was unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, it's a good excuse to go in, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The room the ball entered must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, this is a home invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've got no other choice, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not suspicious people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Something's weird about this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I can't put my finger on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The toy cars on the shelves...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:16:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and the books...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...are almost all upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did my ball do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe your ball warped the space inside the house, causing a supernatural phenomenon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:24.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}{Of course not!}Mitsuhiko, something {\i1}is{\i0} off,\Nbut don't get too carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ball Genta hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I won't lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:32.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here it comes, Genta{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}! Hit it if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.25,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can hit anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:38.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:39.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.72,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.06,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was a pretty strong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.60,Flashback Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez, Genta hit it {\i1}really{\i0} hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta's ball just happened to\Ngo in through an open window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we heard something smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ball must've hit a vase or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if it's really expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I've already blown my allowance this week...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To know how much whatever we broke costs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'll have to ask whoever lives here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ball should be in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:44.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just if the guy who lives here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...can still talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{And it's only been an hour or two since he died.}Given the rigor mortis{that's rigor mortis, isn't it? -uso.}, he's probably been dead for an hour or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see fragments from a vase\Nscattered around the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he was hit on the back of the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ball I hit bumped into the vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and knocked it onto the guy's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do I do? What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:48.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hit that ball just a few minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not an {\i1}hour{\i0} ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now? What... now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:20:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like your ball hit that vase over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good, right, Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this means someone struck him from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He was hit with this vase
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,while he was looking through this drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know that he\Nwas looking through that drawer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the edge of the drawer. It's dented!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body collapsed on it after he was hit from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'd probably opened the drawer to either put something in or to take something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so smart, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the room next door that confuses me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Most of the toys, models and books on the shelves are turned upside-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the killer did that, then what was it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you kids doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Haramoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that Haramoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} on the floor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haramoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haramoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haramoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the police and an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kids need to clear out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh... Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch my cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, out! Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have to give a report when the police arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:54.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:56.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He didn't have to be that rude to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.75,0:23:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something even stranger about this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the shelves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.84,0:24:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dolls{action figures?}, the miniature cars and the books...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all upside-down!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.39,0:24:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.35,0:24:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haramoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't turn\Nthem upside down, the killer did!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.23,0:24:17.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.19,0:24:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: An unfinished manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, an unfinished manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.45,0:24:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, it's completely blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.79,0:24:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why it's unfinished.
